Were these decisions based on how many people you anticipated would be interested in each page, or based on what pages you thought it was most important for people to see first?

5.18.25  9:48 am   Another very important question! In "hi, i'm steve", the guy said that his name is not steve but at the end of the video he said "bye, i'm steve", did he lie or did he forget?

      it ends the video in the same way it starts, and, it is a rare chance to hear the famous phrase "hi, i'm ____" in a 'bye' variation, which surprisingly i had never heard even once before making this video.
     upon further reflection i can also say that the character is giving you mixed messages, from the beginning. perhaps one of the things this video can demonstrate is what it feels like to get mixed messages
